name: AleafAsia International
overview:
AleafAsia International is the Manpower recruitment division of AleafAsia Group which is registered in the Sri Lanka Bureau of Foreign Employment SLBFE with the license number 2642. AleafAsia are keen in professionalism in everything we do and focused on supplying skilled an semi-skilled manpower recruitment services to the Middle East and Malaysia for all sectors.

AleafAsia aims to provide a Total Recruitment Solution to their clients and work to ensure a successful recruitment. AleafAsia has been successfully recruiting manpower for companies worldwide with some of the best available workers who seek career opportunities.
